 />\n<br />\n定係你都同班屈毛一樣亂咁標籤人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲好意思話人屈毛，自己咪做緊本質一樣嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:37:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T17:13:41.000Z","msg":"咁你言下之意係指 應該去六四？<br />\n好多人都唔去六四你唔屌佢地on9？<br />\n係屌學生？仲係到屈人地本土港獨狗？<br />\n去六四係咪寫到明必須出席？如果唔係就犯法？<br />\n<br />\n不如你解釋下唔去六四點中支國共黨計？<br />\n即係自己血腥震壓完，唔俾人提起單嘢，捉撚曬所有尋求事實真相嘅人，又否認有殺人，冇事發生<br />\n<br />\n但同時間又想香港人去六四，記念自己當年有幾凶殘暴戾咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到底邊個先係衝出嚟柒？"},{"pid":"3b90067092fd6ebc5d15c95ed8a734d93fa9d224","tid":670791,"uid":115106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6901b4795d8197e916cb289f10945428bb50479","tid":670791,"uid":22231,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"f02f63e3deaccf69a72b76ba2fe6964358f5eaaf","tid":670791,"uid":86841,"like":3,"dislike":26,"score":-23,"quote":{"pid":"d014138637fd1282247a77e22bff63f2283d1123","tid":670791,"uid":115106,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:33:35.000Z","msg":"啱啊<br />\n六四發生左之後，當年大把人都屌㗎<br />\n梁振英都有份喎，<br />\n<br />\n佢又唔參加六四，咁樣佢係咪本土港獨狗？<br />\n<br />\n定係你都同班屈毛一樣亂咁標籤人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲好意思話人屈毛，自己咪做緊本質一樣嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:37:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:54:35.000Z","msg":"秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T17:14:46.000Z","msg":"秒你老母<br />\n有嘢就講啦，人地jr都仲好過你<br />\n起碼唔會擺低隻字就走